CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Q/C Technologies, Inc. is a pioneering quantum computing infrastructure company at the forefront of next-generation energy-efficient, high-performance computing solutions. Formerly TNF Pharmaceuticals, we completed a strategic transformation in September 2025 to focus on bridging computing paradigms through cutting-edge photonic computing technology. Our company holds exclusive global rights to LightSolver's revolutionary light-speed laser processing unit (LPU), positioning us uniquely in the quantum-class computing market for cryptocurrency and advanced computational applications.
